1 step - Take the dough out and roll it into a circle
2 step - Puff out the edge of the dough so the crust is thicker at the edge
3 step - Pre-heat oven to 250-260 degrees C. (Remember to put a pizza stone in the oven)
4 step - Put on the pizza sauce, cheese, and toppings.
5 step - Put the pizza on the pizza stone in the oven.
6 step - Bake for 30 minutes or until pizza is crispy and golden brown. (make sure you don't burn the toppings)
7 step - Try putting the toppings on the pizza differently to make the pizza look cool! (you can also change the shape of your pizza such as square or triangle)
8 step - Enjoy your homemade pizza!!!